    <para id="delete_me">For each of the following, you will first identify it as one of three types of problem:</para><list id="element-84" list-type="bulleted"><item>No <m:math>
<m:mi>x</m:mi>
</m:math> under a radical, so donâ€™t square both sides.</item>
<item><m:math>
